            <title><![CDATA[【#仅靠症状发现癌症靠谱吗#[思考]】#肿瘤早期患者一般没有症状#没有症状就不会得癌症吗？实际上，不少患者都是出现了一些不舒服的症状才去医院就诊，那么，这种...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BB%85%E9%9D%A0%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E9%9D%A0%E8%B0%B1%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BB%85%E9%9D%A0%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E9%9D%A0%E8%B0%B1%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#仅靠症状发现癌症靠谱吗#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[思考]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_sikao-ff9602dd08.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%82%BF%E7%98%A4%E6%97%A9%E6%9C%9F%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E6%B2%A1%E6%9C%89%E7%97%87%E7%8A%B6%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#肿瘤早期患者一般没有症状#</span></a>没有症状就不会得癌症吗？实际上，不少患者都是出现了一些不舒服的症状才去医院就诊，那么，这种仅凭症状和感觉就判断自己有无患癌的方法靠谱吗？专家介绍，一个小小的瘤子，在人体巨大的脏器前面，除非它发展到晚期，一般是没有症状的。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%9F%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%99%8C%E7%97%87%E4%B8%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%B0%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E6%99%9A%E6%9C%9F%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#为什么癌症一发现就是晚期#</span></a> <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4885032368799853" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网科技的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/001PogqUly1hchzc1628yj60hs0a83zf02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/EVHSv35Dlx084hakJYSA01041200cRPy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=640x368.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680253173&amp;ssig=a0sZWJhjyg&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/uYsAS91Zlx084hakGq7S01041200bsPC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=624x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680253173&amp;ssig=EcnHW8H995&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4885032368799853&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
